c: 14
v: 10
t: "Their messengers said: \"Is there any doubt about God, the Originator of Heaven and Earth? He invites you in order to forgive you some of your offences and to postpone things for you during a specific period.\" They said: \"You are only human beings like ourselves! You want to divert us from what our forefathers have been worshipping, so bring us some clear authority"